It aims to provide information useful before, during, and after the conference. Before the Conference Where will the conference take place? The conference will be held at Alpexpo, espace 1968 in the south of Grenoble. The venue is a bit out of the city centre but is well served by public transport, bike paths, and roads. title: Snowcamp presentation
content: Snowcamp The conference driving you (wal)nuts What is SnowCamp? First and foremost, it's a high-level technical conference that focuses on innovation. SnowCamp brings IT professionals and researchers together to discuss today's and tomorrow's technologies. SnowCamp is a unique concept: day-long workshops on Wednesday, to learn or improve a certain technology; a more classical conference on Thursday and Friday, and a socializing and relaxing day on the snow, in the mountains, on Saturday.
